title: Grateful Dead Live at Philadelphia Civic Center on 1984-04-21
description:
Set 1

Alabama Getaway-> Promised Land, Friend Of The Devil, Me & My Uncle, Mexicali Blues, West L.A. Fadeaway, Minglewood Blues, Tennessee Jed, Looks Like Rain-> Deal

Set 2

Help On The Way-> Slipknot!-> Franklin's Tower-> Playin' In The Band-> China Doll-> Don't Need Love-> Drums-> Wharf Rat-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: Brokedown Palace

reviews.review_text:
My First My first show. Not bad first show for 84.
Thanks to Kevin Tobin for this fine matrix.
We were without even a SBD for this show for the longest time. Finally a SBD shows up, and Kevin almost immediately takes it to the next level.
First show bias aside, this is probably a top 10 show for 84.

Great Run in. Philly Love this show, and I was not at any of them. 
Very good, The boys came to play these shows and they all rock IMO.
